00:42: You can paste it by right clicking into the Rich Text Editor and selecting paste or

00:46: using the keyboard shortcut Ctrl + V on a PC or command + V

00:50: on a Mac.

00:52: To upload an image from the toolbar click the image icon.

00:56: From the drop-down menu select the upload image option.

01:00: Alternatively, you can embed images from the menu bar.

